{"tid":1841483,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[代po] 有班巴打將會免費派口罩","createTime":"2020-01-25T09:34:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T17:15:53.000Z","uid":214644,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"9cd48601da0345d53cc542a57c711255f67eae77","tid":1841483,"uid":214644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T09:34:38.000Z","msg":"轉發素人快報<br />\n<br />\n麻煩分享 感謝各位￼￼<br />\n<br />\n本快報會在一星期內去日本大量採購口罩<br />\n會在旺角 尖沙咀 銅鑼灣 免費派發<br />\n每人最多拎5個<br />\n大約會￼採購200盒回香港<br />\n全部免費派發<br />\n麻煩分享比更多有需要嘅人知道<br />\n<br />\n最後政府唔做更多預防措施<br />\n唯有靠我哋大家自己努力<br />\n發災難財死全家<br />\n祝大家新年快樂 ￼身體健康<br />\n<br />\n今次藍色黃色￼￼￼都不分 大家都係香港人<br />\n<br />\n如果有更多途徑可以採購口罩 麻煩留言給我<br />\n資金有限￼￼￼ 只想出一分力<br />\n￼￼<br />\n<br />\nps.圖片是借用連登的￼￼ 香港人加油<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大約會派10000個，暫定28號喺日本買，31號開始派，到時可能需要人手幫手派<br />\n<br />\n&quot;口罩免費派發 唔會收任何費用 <br />\n我唔想比人覺得我哋呃錢 好麻煩的<br />\n另外問吓大家有冇其他意見<br />\n例如買邊種口罩 或者用任何渠道都得<br />\n最緊要無伏 同埋唔幫襯瘟疫財嘅人&quot;<br />\n<br />\n想知多啲可以去佢地facebook問 ［素人日報］"},{"pid":"1b41783e8849c27b18ed01825ac6bca4d2c55b5f","tid":1841483,"uid":200288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T09:35:58.000Z","msg":"gchi"},{"pid":"6d19a88187aa40233f4cfc373e2154b2376ad24c","tid":1841483,"uid":199401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T09:36:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9619601c58b72ff8d53c8675f3cd2ea6136cbfd","tid":1841483,"uid":41512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T09:37:41.000Z","msg":"有心，支持你哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f49583c2c7f398143df43afc47edc24fd7495edd","tid":1841483,"uid":158422,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T09:45:21.000Z","msg":"多謝<br />\n不過一人得5個，兩日都用完"},{"pid":"57dfda402fda089a12c4a45175bbf1ffb183b74c","tid":1841483,"uid":80503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f49583c2c7f398143df43afc47edc24fd7495edd","tid":1841483,"uid":158422,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T09:45:21.000Z","msg":"多謝<br />\n不過一人得5個，兩日都用完"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T09:46:49.000Z","msg":"始終人數多<br />\n可能兩個鐘內已經派哂"},{"pid":"1427968db076c4fd490f469d1764d4549898678d","tid":1841483,"uid":214644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T09:53:20.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"71c6e37e0214c2e14aa0acdd6c34dd80897de8b7","tid":1841483,"uid":93251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T09:53:27.000Z","msg":"真係唔分黃藍?"},{"pid":"27d3185828db81c8ef376b4bba64e05b8e06a433","tid":1841483,"uid":53652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T09:54:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有心"},{"pid":"95480e8c1f2d289da201684ccae9606880cfe426","tid":1841483,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T09:54:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"28204e0312050bf5e141e76fea730bb4ba76d092","tid":1841483,"uid":134466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71c6e37e0214c2e14aa0acdd6c34dd80897de8b7","tid":1841483